Ashley Madison is a Canadian dating website for married people . 
  Founder Noel Biderman wants to raise money from British investors to fund a launch of its services in Russia, Ukraine and the Baltic states . 
  He is betting on Europe's relaxed attitude to extra-marital affairs to list shares on the stock market in London later this year . 
  Ashley Madison boasts 'life is short, have an affair' and claims to be the world's second-largest dating website . 
  Mr Bidersman came up with the idea for the site in the 1990s when he was a sports attorney . 
  He wants to use the money from London to fund launch of services elsewhere in the world . 
 